            <abstract>
              <p>This document, number 
                  twenty in Carlo Conti Rossini's 
                  edition (and therefore CCR 20 
                  according to Bausi's reference).
The document is attested twice, once it 
follows immediately  
CCR 19 <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6326CCR19">ʿAmda Ṣǝyon's donations</ref> 
                  and followed by 
                  <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6328CCR21">CCR 21 </ref>.
 Further, this document was apparently 
 copied with some insignificant changes into a small quire, which  contains a number of documents likely copied from older documents (originals?) in the sixteenth century.
  </p>
